public static <T,C> ObjectArrayTypeInfo<T,C> getInfoFor(TypeInformation<C> componentInfo)
        Creates a new ObjectArrayTypeInfo from a TypeInformation for the component type.

        This must be used in cases where the complete type of the array is not available as a Type or Class.
